INSERT INTO `sys_blog` VALUES (10, 'Last Dance – 伍佰 & China Blue', '1', '<p><footer class=\"entry-footer\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; display: block; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); color: rgba(51, 51, 51, 0.7); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 1.6rem; line-height: 1.5; padding: 41.2625px 82.525px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"posted-on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 16px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px 1em 0px 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"></span></footer></p><div class=\"entry-content\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: &quot;Noto Serif&quot;, serif; font-size: 19px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px 82.525px 82.525px; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 19px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.6842em; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">看剧时获悉这首歌。来自前几集疯狂吐槽，从安平十三妹开始渐入佳境，看完后直接在豆瓣给到满星的台剧《想见你》。<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">NAS 24小时不间断下载再加上疫情在家，最近影视剧看的比较多，把《命运石之门0》给补完后，没想到立刻还能碰到一部类似题材且同样精彩的真人剧，让从不看台湾偶像剧的我大吃一惊。不仅如此，那么大年纪了看完还能有点小中毒，程度不轻，一整年没更博客的我都又上线了。</p><div class=\"wp-block-group\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 19px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 19px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><p class=\"has-text-align-center\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 19px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.6842em; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center;\">歌曲地址：<a href=\"https://www.xiami.com/song/59454\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; font-family: inherit; font-size: 19px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-decoration: none;\">https://www.xiami.com/song/59454</a></p><p class=\"has-text-align-center\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 19px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.6842em; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"https://player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid=84128983&amp;cid=143914094&amp;page=1\" scrolling=\"no\" border=\"0\" frameborder=\"no\" framespacing=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" __idm_id__=\"752122881\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 19px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;\"></iframe></p></div></div><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 19px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.6842em; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">音乐本身没有太多刻意突出的片段，整个旋律都比较平缓，一耳就能听出的90年代风格也说不上是特色。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 19px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.6842em; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">但是歌曲和剧情相当契合，几乎每一句歌词都能在剧中有所体现。歌曲所说的是离别前的最后一支舞，而歌曲响起的时候又是在过去相见的开始。“所以暂时将你眼睛闭了起来”，“将美丽的回忆慢慢重来”，“明天之后不知道面前的你是否依然爱我”，短短几句基本贯彻了这部剧的主要情节。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 19px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.6842em; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">毒就毒在在时空交织的过程中，有很多切实发生的故事和记忆，最后总会消逝，<strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 19px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">结束和新的开始永远是这物理世界的规律</strong>。对影片中的人来说是这样，对影片外的我们也是如此。观影也是离别的过程，一部让人深深代入的影片结束之时，就是你与影片中人物的永久分离，最后带着这份&lt;共同&gt;记忆的，也只有你一个人。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 19px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.6842em; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">离别是痛苦的，即使只是一对小情侣短时间分离两地，也能让两人哭个泪眼婆娑。疫情之下，不知有多少人是突然的永别，也难以想象这份悲伤有多么巨大。网上看到一句话，说，<strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 19px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 700; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">说不定你所遇之人，也是打破了一个个闭环才能与你相见，定要好好珍惜。</strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 19px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">当然了，是要以快乐的心情去珍惜这一切。同款耳机 UiiSii 云仕 U8 已到货，配上 Sony Walkman WM-2 的 n 代继承者 WM1A，有那味儿了。</p></div>', 'http://luna.vaiwan.com/yttv/profile/upload/2020/10/13/16cbbf1b-e187-4635-9ce0-6d6ec6d928a5.png', '看剧时获悉这首歌。来自前几集疯狂吐槽，从安平十三妹开始渐入佳境，看完后直接在豆瓣给到满星的台剧《想见你》。', '0', 'admin', '2020-10-07 14:21:51', 'admin', '2020-10-13 14:13:48', NULL);
INSERT INTO `sys_blog` VALUES (11, '全力以赴高质量打赢脱贫攻坚战！', '4', '<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 10px auto 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; outline: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 27px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: simsun, arial;\">10月12日上午，市长曹路宝到挂钩帮扶的经济薄弱村响水县徐洪村走访慰问困难群众、调研脱贫攻坚工作，强调要深入学习贯彻习近平总书记重要讲话精神，始终坚持以人民为中心，大力实施乡村振兴战略，以有效措施巩固脱贫、防止返贫，奋力夺取脱贫攻坚战的最终胜利。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 10px auto 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; outline: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 27px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: simsun, arial;\">遍野黄金稻，满目丰收景。曹路宝来到小尖镇徐洪村低收入农户家中，送上市委市政府的关心和温暖。陈永夫妇长期患病，曹路宝勉励他们坚定信心，相信生活会越来越好。82岁的季言法动过3次手术，行动不便；汪秀云今年77岁，丈夫、儿子患病去世，独自一人生活。曹路宝仔细询问生活情况，要求镇村负责同志重点关注特别困难群众，精准帮扶易贫返贫群体，确保在全面脱贫奔小康的路上一个不少、一户不落。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 10px auto 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; outline: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 27px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: simsun, arial;\">在徐洪村党群服务中心，曹路宝主持召开座谈会，与县、镇、村负责同志和群众代表深入交流，了解脱贫攻坚工作情况，对当地干群联系紧密、村容村貌越来越好、群众生活条件改善表示肯定。他强调，今年是决胜全面小康、决战脱贫攻坚的收官之年，各级干部要深入贯彻落实党和国家决策部署，深入基层听民声，进村入户访民情，帮助解决实际困难，坚决打赢脱贫攻坚战。小尖镇、徐洪村要充分发挥区位交通优势，围绕主干道路发展服务业等产业，推动乡村全面振兴，以提升整体发展水平带动脱贫。要更大力度推动农民住房条件改善，切实转变思想观念，按照市委市政府明确要求，鼓励群众进城入镇，嵌入式、插花式建设集中居住点，推动新老村庄有机融合。要创造更多就业创业机会，鼓励村民返乡兴业，激发脱贫内生动力，多措并举扩大增收渠道，以脱贫攻坚的过硬工作成果交上一份满意答卷。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 10px auto 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; outline: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 27px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: simsun, arial;\">204国道改道后穿越徐洪村，曹路宝对照图纸现场察看工程建设进度，了解线路走向、服务区选址等情况，要求高标准高质量建设，确保这条幸福大道早日通车。他指出，响水县要顺应204国道改道带来的城市格局变化，转变发展思路，推动县城与小尖镇相向而行、一体化发展，形成整体发展良好格局。曹路宝还察看了陈家港镇六港村新型社区和草港河道疏浚等项目建设，肯定了响水按流域治理乡村河道的思路与工作成效，要求加快完善配套设施，加强农村河道治理力度，努力打造农村新型社区样板。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 10px auto 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; outline: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 27px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: simsun, arial;\">市政府秘书长郭玉生参加。</p>', 'http://luna.vaiwan.com/yttv/profile/upload/2020/10/11/1c92565f-396a-4b09-bdb9-32631f2f6dc4.JPG', '10月12日上午，市长曹路宝到挂钩帮扶的经济薄弱村响水县徐洪村走访慰问困难群众、调研脱贫攻坚工作，强调要深入学习贯彻习近平总书记重要讲话精神，始终坚持以人民', '0', 'admin', '2020-10-06 15:57:11', 'admin', '2020-10-13 12:05:45', NULL);
INSERT INTO `sys_blog` VALUES (12, '世界上8个最惊心动魄的景点', '2', '<p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">小伙伴们，每到假期是不是都有些烦躁呢？因为不知道要怎么度过，想要出去玩时，但是一想到那些景点人满为患就瞬间没了兴致。不过，还是有一些风景独到的地方并没有那么多人哟。如果你不恐高，够勇敢，想要看到不一样的风景的话，就仔细看看今天置顶表情小编给你介绍的世界上令人惊心动魄的八个景点吧！</p><h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); margin: 16px 0px; font-size: 18px; padding: 10px 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238);\">挪威布道石</h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><img title=\"世界上8个最惊心动魄的景点(图1)\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-8691\" src=\"http://www.wenib.com/uploads/ueditor/20190221/5c6e03a7583e0.png\" alt=\"世界上8个最惊心动魄的景点--置顶表情\" width=\"700\" height=\"880\" data-tag=\"bdshare\" style=\"max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto 20px; display: block; height: auto;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><img title=\"世界上8个最惊心动魄的景点(图2)\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-8692\" src=\"http://www.wenib.com/uploads/ueditor/20190221/5c6e03a759514.png\" alt=\"世界上8个最惊心动魄的景点--置顶表情\" width=\"700\" height=\"522\" data-tag=\"bdshare\" style=\"max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto 20px; display: block; height: auto;\"><br>地处挪威南部，靠近斯塔万格市的吕瑟峡湾中部，是一道悬崖断壁，高604米，直立于峡湾深处的崇山峻岭中，顶部有25平方米的平台，在这里，你可以俯瞰蜿蜒美丽的峡湾，远处起伏苍翠的山峦，不过，这个平台周围是没有围栏的，所以如果你没有足够的心理准备还是不要上去哦！</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;</p><h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); margin: 16px 0px; font-size: 18px; padding: 10px 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238);\">挪威奇迹石</h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><img title=\"世界上8个最惊心动魄的景点(图3)\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-8693\" src=\"http://www.wenib.com/uploads/ueditor/20190221/5c6e03a75a13a.png\" alt=\"世界上8个最惊心动魄的景点--置顶表情\" width=\"700\" height=\"525\" data-tag=\"bdshare\" style=\"max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto 20px; display: block; height: auto;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><img title=\"世界上8个最惊心动魄的景点(图4)\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-8694\" src=\"http://www.wenib.com/uploads/ueditor/20190221/5c6e03a75d918.png\" alt=\"世界上8个最惊心动魄的景点--置顶表情\" width=\"700\" height=\"875\" data-tag=\"bdshare\" style=\"max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto 20px; display: block; height: auto;\"><br>座落于挪威谢拉格山，是世界著名的平衡石。挪威谢拉格山海拔为1110米，奇迹石位于984米高的地方，像楔子一样卡在两块巨大的岩石之间，面积约5平方米，下面就是万丈深渊，而且岩石周围也没有防护措施，所以它也被称为“勇敢者之石”。如果你敢上去，谷底的壮丽风光你就会一览无余哟。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;</p><h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); margin: 16px 0px; font-size: 18px; padding: 10px 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238);\">挪威山妖舌</h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><img title=\"世界上8个最惊心动魄的景点(图5)\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-8695\" src=\"http://www.wenib.com/uploads/ueditor/20190221/5c6e03a75e379.png\" alt=\"世界上8个最惊心动魄的景点--置顶表情\" width=\"700\" height=\"466\" data-tag=\"bdshare\" style=\"max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto 20px; display: block; height: auto;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><img title=\"世界上8个最惊心动魄的景点(图6)\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-8696\" src=\"http://www.wenib.com/uploads/ueditor/20190221/5c6e03a761674.png\" alt=\"世界上8个最惊心动魄的景点--置顶表情\" width=\"700\" height=\"544\" data-tag=\"bdshare\" style=\"max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto 20px; display: block; height: auto;\"><br>挪威名是Trolltunga，其实就是突出悬空的一块巨大岩石，因形状酷似山妖的舌头而得名。地处挪威中南部Hardanger峡湾中部的Odda小镇，位置比较隐秘，去的游客不多，所以你可以一个人坐在伸出长舌的岩石上远眺峡湾美景，静静沉思，静静享受。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;</p><h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); margin: 16px 0px; font-size: 18px; padding: 10px 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238);\">美国纸片岩石</h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><img title=\"世界上8个最惊心动魄的景点(图7)\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-8697\" src=\"http://www.wenib.com/uploads/ueditor/20190221/5c6e03a762025.png\" alt=\"世界上8个最惊心动魄的景点--置顶表情\" width=\"700\" height=\"525\" data-tag=\"bdshare\" style=\"max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto 20px; display: block; height: auto;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><img title=\"世界上8个最惊心动魄的景点(图8)\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-8698\" src=\"http://www.wenib.com/uploads/ueditor/20190221/5c6e03a762a04.png\" alt=\"世界上8个最惊心动魄的景点--置顶表情\" width=\"700\" height=\"525\" data-tag=\"bdshare\" style=\"max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto 20px; display: block; height: auto;\"><br>位于美国加利福尼亚州的沿海城市圣迭戈附近，这块岩石由于特别薄而得名。有许多游客来到这块看似一折就断的石头上拍照留念，虽然高度只有三米，但是如果把握好角度，就像置身在悬崖边或是云端。虽然距离不高，但是轻松坐在上面也仍然需要勇气。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><br></p>', 'http://luna.vaiwan.com/yttv/profile/upload/2020/10/13/4b8173b3-10b4-4423-8743-21715fcb9fc8.png', '小伙伴们，每到假期是不是都有些烦躁呢？因为不知道要怎么度过，想要出去玩时，但是一想到那些景点人满为患就瞬间没了兴致。不过，还是有一些风景独到的地方并没有那么多人哟。如果你不恐高，够勇敢，想要看到不一样的风景的话，就仔细看看今天置顶表情小编给你介绍的世界上令人惊心动魄的八个景点吧！', '0', 'admin', '2020-10-08 16:24:17', 'admin', '2020-10-13 14:44:10', NULL);
INSERT INTO `sys_blog` VALUES (15, 'The Mandalorian OST (曼达洛人)- Ludwig Goransson', '1', '<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: &quot;Noto Serif&quot;, serif; font-size: 19px; margin-bottom: 1.6842em; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">迪士尼这波是真的强，《曼达洛人》五星无疑了，从分镜原画到音乐都美到爆炸。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: &quot;Noto Serif&quot;, serif; font-size: 19px; margin-bottom: 1.6842em; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Hans Zimmer，Ramin Djawadi，Ludwig Göransson，大场景科幻/魔幻 OST 的三位大佬。</p><p class=\"has-text-align-center\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: &quot;Noto Serif&quot;, serif; font-size: 19px; margin-bottom: 1.6842em; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><iframe src=\"https://player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid=77395893&amp;cid=132396752&amp;page=1\" scrolling=\"no\" border=\"0\" frameborder=\"no\" framespacing=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" __idm_id__=\"236999683\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;\"></iframe></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; font-family: &quot;Noto Serif&quot;, serif; font-size: 19px; margin-bottom: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">46秒直击灵魂的 La·Re，同级别震撼的还有《权力的游戏》主题曲里起始的 So·Do，爱哼曲儿的好像对其有一个共同的称呼，唱做 “噔·噔”。</p>', 'http://luna.vaiwan.com/yttv/profile/upload/2020/10/13/f41001f5-a162-4cf8-b650-7701c9cf4e34.jpeg', 'The Mandalorian OST (曼达洛人)- Ludwig Goransson', '0', 'admin', '2020-10-08 16:24:17', 'admin', '2020-10-13 17:54:24', NULL);
INSERT INTO `sys_blog` VALUES (16, '九寨沟', '2', '<h2 style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 30px; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>景区简介：</h2><p><span style=\'text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>　　九寨沟以翠海、叠瀑、彩林、雪峰、蓝冰、藏情合为九寨沟“六绝”，享有“童话世界”的美誉。作为中国必去且最美的地方之一，九寨沟因有九个藏族村寨而得名，平均海拔在2千米以上，境内</span><a style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 1px; text-align: left; color: rgb(106, 19, 89); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\' href=\"https://www.meet99.com/jingdian-jiuzhaigoufengjingqu-1820.html\">原始森林</a><span style=\'text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>密布，湖泊众多。春之花草，夏之流瀑，秋之红叶，冬之白雪，无不令人叫绝。而这一切，隐居在远离尘嚣的的高原深处，纤尘不染、温柔宁静。蓝天、白云、雪山、森林尽融于瀑布、河、滩，缀成一串串宛若从天而降的珍珠；篝火、烤羊、锅庄伴随着古老的神话传说，传递出藏羌族人民热情豪放的民族性格。</span><br style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><span style=\'text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>　</span></p><h2 style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 30px; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><font face=\"Helvetica\"></font><br style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><span style=\'text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>　　</span><br style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><span style=\'text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>　</span></h2><h2 style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 30px; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><font face=\"Helvetica\"></font><br></h2>', 'http://luna.vaiwan.com/yttv/profile/upload/2020/10/13/604af2d7-e2a4-4f91-9a60-2ce38bf4c098.png', '九寨沟', '0', 'admin', '2020-10-08 16:24:17', 'admin', '2020-10-13 18:20:55', NULL);
INSERT INTO `sys_blog` VALUES (17, '故宫', '2', '<span style=\'text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>北京</span><a style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 1px; text-align: left; color: rgb(106, 19, 89); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\' href=\"https://www.meet99.com/jingdian-ForbiddenCity-111166.html\">故宫</a><span style=\'text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>，世界上现存规模最大、保存最为完整的木质结构的古建筑之一，与法国凡尔赛宫、英国白金汉宫、美国白宫、俄罗斯克里姆林宫并称世界五大宫殿。</span><a style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 1px; text-align: left; color: rgb(106, 19, 89); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\' href=\"https://www.meet99.com/jingdian-ForbiddenCity-111166.html\">故宫</a><span style=\'text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>旧称紫禁城，始建于明成祖朱棣永乐四年（公元1406年），历经14年建成竣工，是中国明、清两代24位皇帝的皇家宫殿，也是中国古代汉族宫廷建筑之精华，无与伦比的建筑杰作。</span><br style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><span style=\'text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>　　整个建筑金碧辉煌，庄严绚丽，均是木结构、黄琉璃瓦顶、青白石底座，饰以金碧辉煌的彩画。宫城周围环绕着高12米，长3400米的宫墙，形式为一长方形城池，墙外有52米宽的护城河环绕，形成一个森严壁垒的城堡。宫内以太和、中和、保和三大殿为中心，沿着一条南北向中轴线排列，并向两旁展开，南北取直，左右对称。这条中轴线不仅贯穿在紫禁城内，而且南达永定门，北到鼓楼、钟楼，贯穿了整个城市，气魄宏伟，规划严整，极为壮观。</span><h2 style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 30px; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>景点分布：</h2><span style=\'text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>　　</span><a style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 1px; text-align: left; color: rgb(106, 19, 89); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\' href=\"https://www.meet99.com/jingdian-ForbiddenCity-111166.html\">故宫</a><span style=\'text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>坐落在北京核心，天安门广场与景山公园之间，占地72万平方米，建筑面积15万平方米，有房屋9999间。</span><a style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 1px; text-align: left; color: rgb(106, 19, 89); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\' href=\"https://www.meet99.com/jingdian-ForbiddenCity-111166.html\">故宫</a><span style=\'text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>博物院藏有大量珍贵文物，据统计总共达1052653件之多，统称有文物100万件，占全国文物总数的1/6。</span><a style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 1px; text-align: left; color: rgb(106, 19, 89); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\' href=\"https://www.meet99.com/jingdian-ForbiddenCity-111166.html\">故宫</a><span style=\'text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>的一些宫殿中设立了综合性的历史艺术馆、绘画馆、分类的陶瓷馆、青铜器馆、明清工艺美术馆、铭刻馆、玩具馆、文房四宝馆、玩物馆、珍宝馆、钟表馆和清代宫廷典章文物展览等，收藏有大量古代艺术珍品，是中国收藏文物最丰富的博物馆。</span><p><br></p>', 'http://luna.vaiwan.com/yttv/profile/upload/2020/10/13/b37301ff-e14c-4481-a3a0-0f6d0ad0a0d9.png', '故宫', '0', 'admin', '2020-10-08 16:24:17', 'admin', '2020-10-13 18:20:42', NULL);
INSERT INTO `sys_blog` VALUES (18, '丽江古城', '2', '<h2 style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 30px; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>景区简介：</h2><p><span style=\'text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>　　丽江古城地处我国西南边陲的云南省西北部，是我国保存最为完好的四大古城之一，也是中国向联合国申报世界文化遗产成功的古城之一。丽江是纳西族的家园，纳西族人民长期以来创造并延续下来的东巴文化，是世界民族文化中的一支奇葩。</span><br style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><span style=\'text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>　　丽江古城又名大研镇，始建于宋末元初（公元13世纪后期）。古城地处云贵高原，海拔2400余米，自古以来就是我国西南交通贸易大动脉“南方丝绸之路”和由西藏入境的“茶马古道”的中转站。古城内木楼青瓦，古街石巷，小桥流水，站在古城东大街上，举头即可遥望玉龙雪山。《一米阳光》、《木府风云》等影视剧都在此取过景。</span></p><h2 style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 30px; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><br></h2><p><span style=\'text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>　　<br></span></p>', 'http://luna.vaiwan.com/yttv/profile/upload/2020/10/13/ee5b764c-c2f5-410b-8016-85a82fb8fe70.png', '丽江古城', '0', 'admin', '2020-10-08 16:24:17', 'admin', '2020-10-13 18:23:41', NULL);
INSERT INTO `sys_blog` VALUES (19, '厦门鼓浪屿岛', '2', '<h2 style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 30px; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>景区简介：</h2><p><span style=\'text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>　　厦门鼓浪屿岛内风光秀丽，完好地保存了大量中外风格各异的建筑物，素有“海上花园”、“万国建筑博览”的美誉，又因为小岛音乐人才辈出，也被称为“钢琴之岛”、“音乐之乡”。鼓浪屿街道短小，纵横交错，是厦门最大的一个卫星岛之一，岛上岩石峥嵘，挺拔雄秀，因长年受海浪扑打，形成许多幽谷和峭崖，沙滩、礁石、峭壁、岩峰。</span><br style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><span style=\'text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>　　鼓浪屿原名“圆沙洲”，别名“圆洲仔”，南宋时期命“五龙屿”明朝改称“鼓浪屿”。因岛西南方海滩上有一块两米多高、中有洞穴的礁石，每当涨潮水涌，浪击礁石，声似擂鼓，人们称“鼓浪石”，鼓浪屿因此而得名。</span></p><h2 style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 30px; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><br></h2>', 'http://luna.vaiwan.com/yttv/profile/upload/2020/10/13/f0383acd-4aac-4636-9b69-24fcf11103a8.png', '厦门鼓浪屿岛', '0', 'admin', '2020-10-08 16:24:17', 'admin', '2020-10-13 18:25:24', NULL);
INSERT INTO `sys_blog` VALUES (20, '黄山', '2', '<h2 style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 30px; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>景区简介：</h2><p><span style=\'text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>　　黄山为三山五岳中的三山之一，被誉为“天下第一奇山”，黄山风景区位于中国东部安徽省南部，其中精华部分为154平方公里，号称“五百里黄山”，区内无处不景，无景不奇，尤以奇松、怪石、云海、温泉“四绝”著称于世。</span><br style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><span style=\'text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>　　黄山原名黟山，因峰岩青黑，遥望苍黛而名。后因传说轩辕黄帝曾在此炼丹，故改名为“黄山”。明朝旅行家徐霞客登临黄山时，曾对黄山的秀丽这样赞叹：“薄海内外之名山，无如徽之黄山。登黄山，天下无山，观止矣！”</span></p><h2 style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 30px; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><br></h2>', 'http://luna.vaiwan.com/yttv/profile/upload/2020/10/13/8605fe7f-ee8a-46bb-9d24-7f801d7dfa1a.png', '黄山', '0', 'admin', '2020-10-08 16:24:17', 'admin', '2020-10-13 18:29:51', NULL);
INSERT INTO `sys_blog` VALUES (21, '杭州西湖', '2', '<h2 style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 30px; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>景区简介：</h2><p><span style=\'text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>　　杭州西湖是我国著名的旅游胜地，也被誉为“人间天堂”，是全国十大风景名胜之一，已被列入《世界遗产名录》。西湖古称“钱塘湖”，又名“西子湖”，位于浙江省杭州市，水面面积约4.37平方公里，湖岸周长15公里。西湖古迹遍布，拥有国家重点文物保护单位文物保护点和各类专题博物馆点缀其中，为之增色。《新白娘子传奇》、《白蛇传》、《青蛇》、《秋瑾》、《两宫皇太后》、《梅花三弄之水云间》等影片也均在杭州西湖取景拍摄。</span><br style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><span style=\'text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>　　西湖以秀丽的湖光山色和众多的名胜古迹闻名中外，以湖为主体，以植物造景为主，辅以亭、台、楼、阁、廊、榭、桥、汀，“天下西湖三十六，就中最美是杭州”。园林布局借真山真水、历史文化、神话传说，把山外有山、湖中有湖、景外有景、园中有园的风光点缀得淋漓致。西湖又是著名的历史人文荟萃之地。年过半百的伟大诗人白居易来到美丽的杭州任刺史，在看到西湖山水时，精神为之一振。苏东坡在杭期间，赈灾安民、治理河道，筑就了今天的这道沟通西湖南北的举世闻名的——苏堤。民族英雄岳飞、于谦、张煌言和辛亥革命烈士徐锡麟、秋瑾、陶成章等埋骨于此间青山绿水之间。西湖还和古代灿烂的文化联结融合，遍布南北山区的古代石窟造像，景点中的碑刻和建筑，都是中国艺术的瑰宝。</span><br></p>', 'http://luna.vaiwan.com/yttv/profile/upload/2020/10/13/0966c0b7-36de-4cc0-b915-8d6242fc7732.png', '杭州西湖', '0', 'admin', '2020-10-08 16:24:17', 'admin', '2020-10-13 18:26:41', NULL);
INSERT INTO `sys_blog` VALUES (22, '颐和园', '2', '<h2 style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 30px; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>景区简介：</h2><p><span style=\'text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>　　颐和园是中国现存规模最大、保存最完整的皇家园林，也是保存得最完整的一座皇家行宫御苑，被誉为皇家园林博物馆。园区利用</span><a style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 1px; text-align: left; color: rgb(106, 19, 89); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\' href=\"https://www.meet99.com/jingdian-yiheyuan-24.html\">昆明湖</a><span style=\'text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>、万寿山为基址，以杭州西湖风景为蓝本，汲取江南园林的某些设计手法和意境而建成的一座大型天然山水园，与承德避暑山庄、苏州拙政园、苏州留园并称中国四大名园。</span><br style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><span style=\'text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>　　颐和园前身为清漪园，清朝乾隆皇帝继位以前，在北京西郊一带，建起了四座大型皇家园林。乾隆十五年（1750年），乾隆皇帝为孝敬其母孝圣皇后动用448万两白银在这里改建为清漪园，形成了从现清华园到香山长达二十公里的皇家园林区。咸丰十年（1860年），清漪园被英法联军焚毁。光绪十四年（1888年）重建，改称颐和园，作消夏游乐地。光绪二十六年（1900年），颐和园又遭“八国联军”的破坏，珍宝被劫掠一空。清朝灭亡后，颐和园在军阀混战和国民党统治时期，又遭破坏。</span><br></p>', 'http://luna.vaiwan.com/yttv/profile/upload/2020/10/13/c7ca05d7-de3f-4151-b763-709e0e3a7f28.png', '颐和园', '0', 'admin', '2020-10-08 16:24:17', 'admin', '2020-10-13 18:31:14', NULL);
INSERT INTO `sys_blog` VALUES (23, '上海东方明珠', '2', '<h2 style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 30px; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>景区简介：</h2><p><span style=\'text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>　　上海东方明珠是上海市中心最耀眼的摩天建筑之一，也是上海的地标性建筑之一。东方明珠即东方明珠广播电视塔，坐落在浦东新区陆家嘴黄浦江畔，由上海现代建筑设计有限公司设计。电视塔于1991年7月30日奠基，1994年竣工，高467.9米，由11个大小不一的球体串联一体，其设计来源于“大珠小珠落玉盘”的美妙意境。登上三个主球体，可站在不同的高度品赏浦江两岸的城市风光，尤其站在259米高的全视角全透明高空观光廊上，以“空中漫步”的独特方式欣赏申城全景。而夜晚登临观光层感受“不夜城”夜幕下的绚彩，更是难忘的享受。</span><br style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><span style=\'text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>　　东方明珠塔每年接待来自于五洲四海中外宾客280多万人次，是集观光、餐饮、购物、娱乐、游船、会展、历史陈列、广播电视发射等多功能于一体的综合性旅游文化景点，荣列上海十大新景观之一。如今，东方明珠不仅仅局限于电视塔、观光塔，也是很多重大活动的举办场所，如元旦登高、地球一小时、文化活动等等，成为人们休闲生活的一部分。</span></p><h2 style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 30px; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>景点分布：</h2><p><span style=\'text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>　　东方明珠共有四个观光层。350米的太空舱是上海最高的观光层；263米观光层是俯瞰上海城市全景的最佳场所，浦西3000多栋高层建筑和浦东新建的1000多栋高层建筑，尽收眼底；259米观光层是上海独一无二的室内外观光层；90米观光廊是欣赏外滩万国建筑群的最佳地点。</span><br></p>', 'http://luna.vaiwan.com/yttv/profile/upload/2020/10/13/c80188d5-aa7c-4951-bafe-9447c28e3ae2.png', '上海东方明珠', '0', 'admin', '2020-10-08 16:24:17', 'admin', '2020-10-13 18:32:29', NULL);
INSERT INTO `sys_blog` VALUES (24, '乐山大佛', '2', '<h2 style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 30px; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>景区简介：</h2><p><span style=\'text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>　　</span>乐山<a style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 1px; text-align: left; color: rgb(106, 19, 89); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\' href=\"https://www.meet99.com/jingdian-leshandafo-3123.html\">大佛</a><span style=\'text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>景区集聚了乐山山水人文景观的精华，是世界文化与自然双遗产，闻名遐迩的旅游胜地。</span><a style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 1px; text-align: left; color: rgb(106, 19, 89); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\' href=\"https://www.meet99.com/jingdian-leshandafo-3123.html\">乐山大佛</a><span style=\'text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>地处乐山市市中区，景区面积18平方公里。山上茂林修竹终年葱茏，山下三江汇聚，享有西南山水之冠的美誉，为历代文人墨客所咏赞。其核心的大佛景观通高71米，是唐代摩崖造像艺术的精品，也是世界上最大的石刻弥勒佛坐像，造型庄严，做工细致，堪称人类艺术一大瑰宝。而大佛所在的</span><a style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 1px; text-align: left; color: rgb(106, 19, 89); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\' href=\"https://www.meet99.com/jingdian-leshandafo-3136.html\">凌云山</a><span style=\'text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>又与背后的</span><a style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 1px; text-align: left; color: rgb(106, 19, 89); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\' href=\"https://www.meet99.com/jingdian-leshandafo-28385.html\">乌尤山</a><span style=\'text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>、龟城山构成了一尊巨形睡佛，可谓景中有景，佛在佛中，堪称千古奇观。</span><br style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><span style=\'text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>　　</span><br></p>', 'http://luna.vaiwan.com/yttv/profile/upload/2020/10/13/3c0a42af-ca06-4675-9731-b4c747bea08d.png', '乐山大佛', '0', 'admin', '2020-10-08 16:24:17', 'admin', '2020-10-13 18:35:46', NULL);
INSERT INTO `sys_blog` VALUES (25, '千岛湖', '2', '<h2 style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 30px; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>景区简介：</h2><p><span style=\'text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>　　千岛湖是世界上岛屿最多的湖，也是中国面积最大的森林公园，以1078个岛屿入选中国世界纪录协会，创造了世界之最。千岛湖景区即新安江水库，总面积982平方公里，其中湖区面积573平方公里，是1959年我国建造的第一座自行设计、自制设备的大型水力发电站——新安江水力发电站而拦坝蓄水形成的人工湖，为国家一级水体，堪称杭州的“后花园”。</span><br style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><span style=\'text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>　　大大小小形态各异的岛屿分布有疏有密，罗列有致。群集处形成众岛似连非连，湖面被分隔得宽窄不同、曲折多变、方向难辨，形成湖上迷宫的特色景观，更有百湖岛、百岛湖、珍珠岛等千姿百态的群岛、列岛。岛屿稀疏处，湖面开阔、深远、浩渺，宛如海面。同时，这里的森林覆盖率达95%，有“绿色千岛湖”之称，植物种类非常丰富，保存着比较完整、面积较大的阔叶混交林区及千亩田、磨心尖的植物分布群落等；94种鱼类、90种鸟类、百余种野生动物等都栖息在这里，可开展丰富多彩的展览、垂钓、围捕等特色旅游项目。</span><br></p>', 'http://luna.vaiwan.com/yttv/profile/upload/2020/10/13/3725361e-8a84-45f9-a7c1-3d946ba7125b.png', '千岛湖', '0', 'admin', '2020-10-08 16:24:17', 'admin', '2020-10-13 18:38:29', NULL);
INSERT INTO `sys_blog` VALUES (26, '峨眉山', '2', '<h2 style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 30px; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>景区简介：</h2><p><span style=\'text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>　　峨眉山，“普贤者，佛之长子， 峨眉者， 山之领袖”，是中国四大佛教名山之一、世界自然与文化双遗产，有“峨眉天下秀”之美誉。景区位于四川乐山峨眉山市境内，面积154平方公里，区内山势雄伟，隘谷深幽，飞瀑如帘，</span><a style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 1px; text-align: left; color: rgb(106, 19, 89); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\' href=\"https://www.meet99.com/jingdian-emeishan-110.html\">云海</a><span style=\'text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>翻涌，林木葱茏，浓缩了千万年来自然精华。峨眉山的游览线路就有120余华里，主峰金顶绝壁凌空、高插云霄；震撼的金顶，凌云之巅，世界最高的金佛—四面十方普贤等等震撼着游客的心灵，可谓集天地灵气，映日月光辉。而四季景色各有万千，素有“一山有四季，十里不同天”之妙喻。</span><br style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><span style=\'text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>　　峨眉山是人类文化的宝库，文化遗产极其深厚，被誉为“佛国天堂”。作为普贤菩萨的道场，这里拥有世界上最大的佛教朝拜中心，是佛在人中、人在景中、景在佛中的人间天庭。每年，全国各地朝圣者络绎不绝，且寺内珍藏诸多精美佛教瑰宝，吸引着人们前来一睹其真容。</span><br style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><span style=\'text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>　　山上壮观，山下悠闲。低山区构成了目前中国西部规模最大、功能配套最完善、设施最先进的温泉度假国际会议中心，峨眉山也因此成为集休养、养生、文化、娱乐、观光、美食为一体的全新多功能复合型的魅力新景区。</span><br></p>', 'http://luna.vaiwan.com/yttv/profile/upload/2020/10/13/88a788f0-7d1f-4699-bc0c-e462bcb01e15.png', '峨眉山', '0', 'admin', '2020-10-08 16:24:17', 'admin', '2020-10-13 18:39:47', NULL);
INSERT INTO `sys_blog` VALUES (27, '西藏布达拉宫', '2', '<h2 style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 30px; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>景区简介：</h2><p><span style=\'text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>　　西藏布达拉宫始建于公元7世纪，最初为吐蕃王朝赞普松赞干布为迎娶尺尊公主和文成公主而兴建。1645年（清顺治二年）五世达赖洛桑嘉措重建布达拉宫之后，成为历代达赖喇嘛冬宫居所，以及重大宗教和政治仪式举办地，也是供奉历世达赖喇嘛灵塔之地，旧时西藏政教合一的统治中心。</span><br style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><span style=\'text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>　　布达拉宫是世界上海拔最高，集宫殿、城堡和寺院于一体的宏伟建筑，也是西藏最庞大、最完整的古代宫堡建筑群。整座宫殿具有鲜明的藏式风格，依山而建，气势雄伟，由</span><a style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 1px; text-align: left; color: rgb(106, 19, 89); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\' href=\"https://www.meet99.com/jingdian-budalagong-6536.html\">白宫</a><span style=\'text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>和</span><a style=\'list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 1px; text-align: left; color: rgb(106, 19, 89); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\' href=\"https://www.meet99.com/jingdian-budalagong-6537.html\">红宫</a><span style=\'text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", 微软雅黑, MicrosoftJhengHei, 华文细黑, STHeiti, MingLiu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>及其附属建筑组成。布达拉宫中还收藏了无数的珍宝，堪称是一座艺术的殿堂。布达拉宫，位于拉萨市的中心。</span><br></p>', 'http://luna.vaiwan.com/yttv/profile/upload/2020/10/13/718fdd97-3930-43f5-b2d2-ab6ddd2bec33.png', '西藏布达拉宫', '0', 'admin', '2020-10-08 16:24:17', 'admin', '2020-10-13 18:40:42', NULL);
